br /> - BusLogic driver update<br /> - ncpfs update (I suspect this one requires the new ncpfs tools)<br /><br />I suspect I may _still_ have missed a few patches, so keep pestering me<br />about it if you don't find your favourite patch in the latest kernel.<br /><br />		Linus<br /><br /></pre><div align="center"><div class="shariff" data-services="[&quot;reddit&quot;]" data-theme="grey" data-lang="en" data-backend-url="//shariff.lkml.org/index.php"></div></div></td><td width="32" rowspan="2" class="c" valign="top"><img src="/images/icornerr.gif" width="32" height="32" alt="\" /></td></tr><tr><td align="right" valign="bottom">
